<plot>April is a surrealist and stylish short with a healthy dose of black comedy. April, the film's eponymous heroine, dreams about losing her umbrella, a dream which is the beginning of a bizarre chain of premonitions which will unravel her world, revealing it in a totally new light. As April comes to recognize her increasingly vivid and surreal dreams for the premonitions they are, she is as intrigued by the world they are leading her to as she is scared of their shocking power. An inspected powerful twist is in the tail.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?043938</url></doc>
